{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2067, "height": 2881, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "九", "block_bbox": [163, 2179, 212, 2233], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "doc_title", "block_content": "历次纂修家谱规定", "block_bbox": [803, 236, 1401, 318], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "（一）", "block_bbox": [331, 391, 421, 440], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一、本规定系本族人商议规定，希我全族人共同执行之。", "block_bbox": [327, 454, 1353, 509], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二、杜氏宗谱三十年续一次。", "block_bbox": [326, 523, 855, 576], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三、自十六世到三十世规定字为：宗信克太平国正天心顺官清民自安。", "block_bbox": [326, 591, 1704, 646], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "四、此次财力缺乏，印本较少，家谱不论存放谁家，永远是本族公有之物，不得无故损坏。\n", "block_bbox": [324, 658, 1878, 785], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "五、每年上老坟日期规定为阴历正月二十七。十月一日在祠堂烧寒衣，不得无故旷废。\n", "block_bbox": [326, 800, 1878, 926], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "六、谨遵古制，同族不婚。", "block_bbox": [327, 942, 793, 996], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一九六二年十一月一日", "block_bbox": [1360, 1010, 1803, 1061], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "（二）", "block_bbox": [332, 1151, 423, 1202], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一、杜氏家谱规定三十年续一次。", "block_bbox": [327, 1219, 944, 1270], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二、每年上老坟为清明节，到时各村应选代表参加为好。", "block_bbox": [328, 1286, 1356, 1341], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三、自十六世到三十世的人起名时按规定字叫，字为：宗、信、克、太、平、国、正、天、心、顺、官、清、民、自、安。\n", "block_bbox": [324, 1353, 1879, 1472], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一九八八年", "block_bbox": [1583, 1494, 1808, 1544], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "旧谱凡例", "block_bbox": [1004, 1632, 1290, 1703], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一、自来叙宗谱者，必制世系图，以便明了世系也。然图由表制，有表即可明其世系，兹为精俭节约计，不制世系图。\n", "block_bbox": [326, 1789, 1877, 1905], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二、本谱信则传信，疑则传疑。凡先人之世次名讳坟墓居所，一依旧谱。不敢自作聪明，妄改一字，以还庐山真面目。\n", "block_bbox": [325, 1923, 1870, 2044], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三、本谱凡有子者，则书“子几”。无子而有继子，则书“继子”。如其人已殁，而无后人继承者，则书“乏嗣”。如虽无子嗣而其人尚存者，则不书“乏嗣”，以其有待于后也。\n", "block_bbox": [324, 2062, 1876, 2251], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "四、本谱必严义子之书，恐乱宗也。其先有义子而复生子者，则先书生子、后书义子，以重宗也。\n", "block_bbox": [329, 2269, 1878, 2392], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "五、旧谱原只东西二门。然据传杜坑、孟村、西窑三门亦系本宗迁出，故为补叙。", "block_bbox": [416, 2410, 1877, 2464], "block_id": 20, "block_order": 21}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "公元一九六二年元月一日", "block_bbox": [1320, 2482, 1805, 2534], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 22}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9186397790908813, "coordinate": [324.65960693359375, 2062.10009765625, 1876.978759765625, 2251.41845703125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8948115706443787, "coordinate": [326.3419189453125, 1789.619873046875, 1877.0755615234375, 1905.59033203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8942758440971375, "coordinate": [329.7550048828125, 2269.7783203125, 1878.0418701171875, 2392.634765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8932487368583679, "coordinate": [325.584228515625, 1923.93505859375, 1870.542724609375, 2044.10400390625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8304473757743835, "coordinate": [326.2606201171875, 800.6031494140625, 1878.0338134765625, 926.3443603515625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8249199986457825, "coordinate": [324.17462158203125, 1353.992431640625, 1879.12451171875, 1472.415283203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8170623183250427, "coordinate": [324.3284912109375, 658.1234130859375, 1878.8458251953125, 785.7528076171875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.8085771799087524, "coordinate": [1004.899169921875, 1632.94384765625, 1290.979736328125, 1703.52783203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.765227735042572, "coordinate": [416.376708984375, 2410.85205078125, 1877.607666015625, 2464.91943359375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7433985471725464, "coordinate": [1583.1932373046875, 1494.5599365234375, 1808.4200439453125, 1544.4720458984375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.736932098865509, "coordinate": [1360.916748046875, 1010.122314453125, 1803.441162109375, 1061.98974609375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.735063910484314, "coordinate": [327.8165283203125, 454.68939208984375, 1353.5582275390625, 509.68280029296875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7160090804100037, "coordinate": [328.758056640625, 1286.38037109375, 1356.1688232421875, 1341.55712890625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6931132674217224, "coordinate": [1320.6219482421875, 2482.632568359375, 1805.0838623046875, 2534.656005859375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6845020055770874, "coordinate": [326.8351745605469, 523.2196044921875, 855.817626953125, 576.941162109375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.679961085319519, "coordinate": [326.21173095703125, 591.7067260742188, 1704.89599609375, 646.5222778320312]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6710441708564758, "coordinate": [327.6563720703125, 1219.32763671875, 944.9654541015625, 1270.8193359375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6675563454627991, "coordinate": [327.4234619140625, 942.8167724609375, 793.01953125, 996.9935302734375]}, {"cls_id": 10, "label": "doc_title", "score": 0.6432247757911682, "coordinate": [803.8729858398438, 236.87966918945312, 1401.45458984375, 318.6693420410156]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.6206179857254028, "coordinate": [332.5576171875, 1151.303466796875, 423.10589599609375, 1202.322265625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.573692262172699, "coordinate": [331.0115966796875, 391.5509338378906, 421.6036376953125, 440.3343811035156]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.4141112267971039, "coordinate": [163.02993774414062, 2179.97119140625, 212.54953002929688, 2233.34423828125]}]}, "overall_ocr_res": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[808, 240], [1406, 238], [1406, 317], [808, 319]], [[327, 384], [431, 384], [431, 447], [327, 447]], [[335, 458], [1349, 458], [1349, 505], [335, 505]], [[334, 525], [852, 527], [852, 575], [334, 573]], [[333, 594], [1159, 594], [1159, 644], [333, 644]], [[1197, 598], [1421, 596], [1421, 640], [1198, 642]], [[1457, 592], [1702, 595], [1701, 645], [1457, 642]], [[331, 663], [1878, 658], [1878, 711], [331, 716]], [[327, 727], [450, 730], [448, 794], [326, 791]], [[138, 737], [246, 737], [246, 958], [138, 958]], [[332, 802], [1876, 799], [1876, 853], [332, 856]], [[327, 867], [414, 867], [414, 933], [327, 933]], [[332, 944], [791, 947], [791, 995], [332, 992]], [[1368, 1016], [1802, 1016], [1802, 1060], [1368, 1060]], [[146, 1050], [240, 1051], [237, 1488], [144, 1487]], [[331