]], [[419, 1789], [1874, 1796], [1874, 1844], [418, 1837]], [[333, 1853], [1008, 1857], [1007, 1907], [333, 1903]], [[420, 1923], [1867, 1928], [1867, 1979], [420, 1974]], [[334, 1991], [1011, 1996], [1010, 2047], [334, 2042]], [[423, 2066], [1872, 2066], [1872, 2113], [423, 2113]], [[334, 2131], [1872, 2133], [1872, 2184], [334, 2182]], [[158, 2179], [220, 2179], [220, 2237], [158, 2237]], [[329, 2195], [412, 2201], [407, 2262], [325, 2256]], [[424, 2275], [1873, 2275], [1873, 2322], [424, 2322]], [[335, 2339], [640, 2343], [639, 2397], [335, 2393]], [[423, 2415], [1874, 2416], [1874, 2464], [423, 2463]], [[1330, 2488], [1801, 2488], [1801, 2532], [1330, 2532]]], "rec_boxes": [[808, 238, 1406, 319], [327, 384, 431, 447], [335, 458, 1349, 505], [334, 525, 852, 575], [333, 594, 1159, 644], [1197, 596, 1421, 642], [1457, 592, 1702, 645], [331, 658, 1878, 716], [326, 727, 450, 794], [138, 737, 246, 958], [332, 799, 1876, 856], [327, 867, 414, 933], [332, 944, 791, 995], [1368, 1016, 1802, 1060], [144, 1050, 240, 1488], [331, 1147, 431, 1209], [334, 1219, 941, 1269], [335, 1288, 1353, 1342], [334, 1352, 1877, 1411], [334, 1419, 789, 1474], [1586, 1492, 1808, 1547], [1005, 1630, 1295, 1707], [418, 1789, 1874, 1844], [333, 1853, 1008, 1907], [420, 1923, 1867, 1979], [334, 1991, 1011, 2047], [423, 2066, 1872, 2113], [334, 2131, 1872, 2184], [158, 2179, 220, 2237], [325, 2195, 412, 2262], [424, 2275, 1873, 2322], [335, 2339, 640, 2397], [423, 2415, 1874, 2464], [1330, 2488, 1801, 2532]]}}, "markdown": {"text": "九\n\n# 历次纂修家谱规定\n\n## （一） \n\n一、本规定系本族人商议规定，希我全族人共同执行之。\n\n二、杜氏宗谱三十年续一次。\n\n三、自十六世到三十世规定字为：宗信克太平国正天心顺官清民自安。\n\n四、此次财力缺乏，印本较少，家谱不论存放谁家，永远是本族公有之物，不得无故损坏。\n\n\n\n五、每年上老坟日期规定为阴历正月二十七。十月一日在祠堂烧寒衣，不得无故旷废。\n\n\n\n六、谨遵古制，同族不婚。\n\n一九六二年十一月一日\n\n## （二） \n\n一、杜氏家谱规定三十年续一次。\n\n二、每年上老坟为清明节，到时各村应选代表参加为好。\n\n三、自十六世到三十世的人起名时按规定字叫，字为：宗、信、克、太、平、国、正、天、心、顺、官、清、民、自、安。\n\n\n\n一九八八年\n\n## 旧谱凡例\n\n一、自来叙宗谱者，必制世系图，以便明了世系也。然图由表制，有表即可明其世系，兹为精俭节约计，不制世系图。\n\n\n\n二、本谱信则传信，疑则传疑。凡先人之世次名讳坟墓居所，一依旧谱。不敢自作聪明，妄改一字，以还庐山真面目。\n\n\n\n三、本谱凡有子者，则书“子几”。无子而有继子，则书“继子”。如其人已殁，而无后人继承者，则书“乏嗣”。如虽无子嗣而其人尚存者，则不书“乏嗣”，以其有待于后也。\n\n\n\n四、本谱必严义子之书，恐乱宗也。其先有义子而复生子者，则先书生子、后书义子，以重宗也。\n\n\n\n五、旧谱原只东西二门。然据传杜坑、孟村、西窑三门亦系本宗迁出，故为补叙。\n\n公元一九六二年元月一日", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//96b7bc62-cc98-4ebe-8eca-41c41d507ef3/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A37Z%2F-1%2F%2F6fbf6c3c574a86623d1bb259e53fc87a7062420c5d3d7fab979f85160d043ac8", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//96b7bc62-cc98-4ebe-8eca-41c41d507ef3/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A37Z%2F-1%2F%2F541d64bd3d6224df2c082a5fa8d8dcdf92d4397f6bb8a8d1b3d9396c1596306c", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//96b7bc62-cc98-4ebe-8eca-41c41d507ef3/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A37Z%2F-1%2F%2F5ba36e1f13688ce3c29598761d911a0302170f4bcc9e6f86e7f5fcc4c12131ac", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//96b7bc62-cc98-4ebe-8eca-41c41d507ef3/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A38Z%2F-1%2F%2F621b707c525bb8a2ac6e32cb6395474e558ec39e17b5d8ec2905ab9e9c11d483"}, "inputImage": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//96b7bc62-cc98-4ebe-8eca-41c41d507ef3/input_img_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A37Z%2F-1%2F%2Ff8b3109a345ee6b8bcdf113123f4b26e61d0c259e04e46187b4a223c73f89769"}], "dataInfo": {"width": 2067, "height": 2881, "type": "image"}, "ocrResults": [{"prunedResult": {"model_settings": {"use